  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in Senate", 
    "date": "2017-10-25T04:00:00Z", 
    "text": "Combating the Opioid Epidemic Act\n\nThis bill amends the 21st Century Cures Act to provide additional funds through FY2027 for\u00a0state grants to\u00a0address the opioid abuse crisis.\n\nThe bill provides funds to the Department of Health and Human Services through FY2022 for state grants to conduct research on addiction and pain related to substance misuse."
